      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to deliver peak performance up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is equipped with the M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC), ensuring exceptional lateral grip and suspension response. This example is mechanically robust, having undergone preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator service. While displaying minor aesthetic wear consistent with its mileage, the powertrain and subframe remain in excellent operational order, providing an authentic, visceral M-car experience.",
